Data Flow Explanation

1. User interacts with frontend (search, login, buy).
2. React sends API request to backend.
3. Express validates request and forwards to service layer.
4. Service layer processes logic (cart/order).
5. Mongoose interacts with MongoDB.
6. Data is returned to backend.
7. Backend sends response to frontend.
8. UI updates accordingly.

